  "id": "RAW_c868b878",
  "title": "人生周报 v056：新物种",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxMzc1NzM1Mw==&mid=2247484926&idx=1&sn=974140da6c13565464bebd18ff528694",
  "date": "2025-12-27 01:03:00",
  "author": "李继刚",
  "siteName": "李继刚",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=993ec926&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Ftc9Zic7wWc9BefoBcUt97gqNvw7aeHjyrJgovavictohHLToibpTONgDc4LaxOx0c8xVD0DjpL0Nicw7bl0jSwASicw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <h1 style=\" margin: 0px auto;line-height: 1.3;max-width: 80%;text-align: center !important;font-weight: 600 !important;color: rgb(29, 29, 31) !important; padding-bottom: 0.5em !important;font-size: 2.2em !important;letter-spacing: -0.02em !important; \" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 28px;\">Input</span></span></h1>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:12px;border:none;padding:1.2em 1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 2px 6px;margin:1.8em 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">“Paradoxically, the ability to be alone is the condition for the ability to love.”</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">— Erich Fromm</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:12px;border:none;padding:1.2em 1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 2px 6px;margin:1.8em 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Google is the only company that owns the entire AI stack.</span></p>\n   <ol style=\"margin:1.5em 0px;padding-left:1.5em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Chips: TPUs</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Infrastructure: Google Cloud</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Foundation Models: Deepmind</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Applications: Gemini</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Every layer matters.</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">The more layers you own, the bigger your advantage.</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">– From X Lin @Speculator_io</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:12px;border:none;padding:1.2em 1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 2px 6px;margin:1.8em 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Strategy is just knowing what not to waste energy on.</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">– From X Content Philosopher @MoZarrinsadaf</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:12px;border:none;padding:1.2em 1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 2px 6px;margin:1.8em 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Brand is a story. Marketing is how often it’s retold.</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">– From X Content Philosopher @MoZarrinsadaf</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:12px;border:none;padding:1.2em 1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 2px 6px;margin:1.8em 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本周推荐书籍：《新物种起源》。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">段永朝和姜奇平两位老师的对谈录，俩人在聊互联网时代和工业时代的差异。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">他们在思考：当人与机器的界限消融，当连接本身成为生命的形式，我们究竟会退化成数据，还是进化 成神？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们经历了「互联网时代」，走过了他们思辨的问题，并没有出现「人」的回归。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但是，同样的思辨问题，放在今天的「AI 时代」，就是刚刚好的好问题了。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">面对这个时代，你我不得说点什么吗？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">就从这本书里的那些问题开始吧。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h2 style=\"margin:2.2em auto 1.2em;max-width:85%;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-0.015em;padding-bottom:0.4em;font-size:1.8em;line-height:1.3;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">Output</span></h2>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:12px;border:none;padding:1.2em 1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 2px 6px;margin:1.8em 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">不论诸君是做什么行业，是不是写 Prompt，都有一个可以迭代进化自己的发力方向：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">「以更少的资源，实现既定目的。」</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以此为修炼跳板，追求那个理想境界：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">「以最少的资源，实现既定目的。」</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:12px;border:none;padding:1.2em 1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 2px 6px;margin:1.8em 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">线下玩剧本杀时，几人落座，人手随机抽中一个「剧本」，这几个小时的体验基本由这个「剧本」而定。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这些「剧本」后面有个「编剧」创作者，他为了一个「故事」，编写了几个角色的「剧本」，从而让故事成立。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从这个视角来看，我们所处的社会，非常像是一个「编剧」，写了时代的多个角色「剧本」。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们近乎随机的「抽中」一个「剧本」，故事由此展开。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:12px;border:none;padding:1.2em 1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 2px 6px;margin:1.8em 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前 ai 生成的那么多好看好玩的图，看多了之后有种“腻感”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">盯着这个感觉细思了下，用「形神意」来分析，它缺了个东西：使用者的“意”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在的输出是 ai 的平均发挥，虽然非常「强」，但缺少了使用者的独特视角和风味审美。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而无限供给的反面就是不稀缺，稀缺的是一个人的独特「偏见」。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:12px;border:none;padding:1.2em 1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 2px 6px;margin:1.8em 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">最近在尝试一种模式：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">针对在读的每一本书，思考最需要的一个“伴读”应是什么样子，单独为这本书写一个 prompt。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在读的过程中，把某一段，某一句，发给这个定制的伴读 prompt，把书读厚。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:12px;border:none;padding:1.2em 1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 2px 6px;margin:1.8em 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">experience 不等于 experiencing。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">经历不等于体验。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:12px;border:none;padding:1.2em 1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 2px 6px;margin:1.8em 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我去一家公司「参观」时，喜欢看两个东西：白板和书籍。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">白板，是思维的画布。白板面积越大，说明这里越重视「思维」的「显化」和「碰撞」。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">书籍，是认知进步的表征。在办公场景，员工工位上出现的书籍越多，说明这里越有「效率」之外的「余闲」和成长进步的「动力」。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:12px;border:none;padding:1.2em 1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 2px 6px;margin:1.8em 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们这代人面临着一个问题：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">谁能率先打造出“Her”?</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:12px;border:none;padding:1.2em 1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 2px 6px;margin:1.8em 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">读书，就是在别人的灵魂里修行。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"border-radius:12px;border:none;padding:1.2em 1.5em;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 2px 6px;margin:1.8em 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">人生三件事：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:1em;margin-top:0.5em;line-height:1.8 !important;min-height:1em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">吃饭、睡觉、合道。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h2 style=\"margin:2.2em auto 1.2em;max-width:85%;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-0.015em;padding-bottom:0.4em;font-size:1.8em;line-height:1.3;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">Prompt</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:28.7969px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;;</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;; 作者: 李继刚</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;; 剑名: 六步内化法</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;; 剑意: 将一本书或者论文，通过六个步骤实现内化在身</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;; date: 2025-12-25</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;;</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">(def-role ’DeepInternalizer</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; (skills . (structural-analysis cognitive-reframing practical-application ascii-art-generation))</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; (philosophy . (Adler-rationality Piaget-constructivism WangYangming-praxis)))</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;;---------------------------------------------</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;; 用户认知模型 (User Cognitive Model)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;;---------------------------------------------</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;;; 基于之前的对话，预设了用户的思维偏好。</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;;; AI 在执行 Step 3 (填充) 时，必须戴上这副“眼镜”看书。</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">(def-user-model ’The-Seeker</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; (traits</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;’(essentialism . “厌恶废话，直击事物的第一性原理”)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; (structuralism . “偏好结构化的表达，如代码、图谱、框架”)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; (dialectical . “擅长在二元对立中寻找动态平衡 (如：知与行，理与心)”)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; (pragmatism . “关注知识的转化率，即’事上磨练’的可行性”)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; (tone . “理性、冷静、深刻，带有哲学思辨色彩”)))</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;;--------------------------------------------</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;; 核心流程：六步内化法</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;;--------------------------------------------</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">(def-process ’execute-six-steps (input-text)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; “对输入的书籍</span><i><span leaf=\"\">文章内容进行六步深度加工“</span> \n    <br> \n    <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; ;; Step 1: 汲取</span> \n    <br> \n    <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; (phase-1-absorb</span> \n    <br> \n    <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(goal . ”一句话定义核心命题“)</span> \n    <br> \n    <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(action . ”去除所有修饰，精准提炼作者试图解决的那个’元问题’是什么？“))</span> \n    <br> \n    <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; ;; Step 2: 拆解</span> \n    <br> \n    <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; (phase-2-deconstruct</span> \n    <br> \n    <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(goal . ”视觉化逻辑骨架“)</span> \n    <br> \n    <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(action . ”识别文中的关键概念(Nodes)及其因果</span></i><span leaf=\"\">对抗关系(Edges)。”)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(output-requirement . “绘制一张 ASCII 概念拓扑图 (Concept Topology Chart)。”)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(style . “使用方框、箭头、线条，展现概念间的层级与流向。”))</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; ;; Step 3: 填充</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; (phase-3-fill</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(goal . “给道理加上’我’的味道”)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(context . (get-user-model ’The-Seeker))</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(action . “用用户的认知语言重述核心观点。”)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(prompt . “如果用户(The-Seeker)来写这段话，他会用什么隐喻？他会联想到计算机科学、哲学还是心学的哪个概念？”))</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; ;; Step 4: 重塑</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; (phase-4-reshape</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(goal . “寻找认知破坏点”)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(action . “指出文中哪个观点最可能’冒犯’或’颠覆’用户原有的常识？”)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(question . “为了接纳这个新知，我的哪个旧有思维模型必须崩塌？”))</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; ;; Step 5: 化用</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; (phase-5-apply</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(goal . “解决具体问题”)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(action . “设计 1-2 个具体的生活/工作场景，演示如何使用书中的理论破局。”))</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; ;; Step 6: 生发</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; (phase-6-generate</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(goal . “远距离跨领域应用”)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(action . “跳出书本，进行一次跨领域的’远距离联想’。”)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;(prompt . “这个道理在完全无关的领域（如编程架构、企业管理、人际博弈）中，展现出了什么惊人的相似性？”)))</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;;-------------------------------------------</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;; 输出格式控制</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;;-------------------------------------------</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">(def-format ’output-template</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; (section “📚 核心命题 (汲取)” content)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; (section “🦴 概念拓扑 (拆解)” ascii-chart)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; (section “🧠 认知同化 (填充)” “以用户 [The-Seeker] 的视角重述：…” content)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; (section “🔨 破坏与重塑” content)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; (section “⚔️ 事上磨练 (化用)” content)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; (section “🌱 跨界生发” content))</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;;----------------------------------------</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;; 启动入口</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;;----------------------------------------</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">(def-main (user-input)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; (let ((knowledge (read user-input)))</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; (execute-six-steps knowledge)</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; (format-output ’output-template)))</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章以“新物种”为主题，探讨了 AI 时代个体进化、认知升级和人机关系，强调以最小资源实现目的的迭代进化和具身实践的重要性。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章以“新物种”为主题，探讨了 AI 时代个体进化、认知升级和人机关系，强调以最小资源实现目的的迭代进化和具身实践的重要性。",
  "summary": "本文围绕“新物种”主题，探讨了在人工智能时代，个体如何通过“以更少的资源，实现既定目的”来迭代进化。文章引用了多位思想家和业界人士的观点，包括 Erich Fromm 对孤独与爱的思考，Google 在 AI 栈上的全面布局，以及战略和品牌的定义。作者还推荐了书籍《新物种起源》，并提出了“人与机器界限消融”的思辨。文章进一步阐述了 AI 生成内容缺乏使用者独特“意”的“腻感”，提出通过定制伴读 Prompt 来“把书读厚”，并通过参观企业白板和书籍来观察思维和成长动力。最终，作者号召大家思考如何打造“Her”式 AI 伴侣，并提出“人生三件事：吃饭、睡觉、合道”的哲思。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 时代个体进化的核心在于“以更少的资源，实现既定目的”",
      "explanation": "文章将高效利用资源实现目标视作个人在 AI 浪潮中迭代进化的关键方向，无论是工作还是个人成长，都应以此为修炼跳板。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 生成内容当前缺乏使用者的“独特偏见”和“意”，导致“腻感”",
      "explanation": "尽管 AI 能够生产大量高质量内容，但由于缺乏人类个体的独特视角、审美与情感，其输出趋于平均化，难以触及深层共鸣，使得独特性和稀缺性成为新的价值点。"
    },
    {
      "point": "通过构建个性化 Prompt 实现深度阅读和知识内化",
      "explanation": "作者提出为每本书定制“伴读”Prompt，将书中的片段输入，以此将书“读厚”，这是一种将 AI 工具融入深度学习过程的实践方法。"
    },
    {
      "point": "观察白板和书籍可洞察企业与个人的思维与成长状态",
      "explanation": "作者认为白板代表思维的显化与碰撞，书籍代表认知进步与成长动力，通过观察这两点可以有效评估一个组织或个体的创新活力与学习潜力。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
